### Login as admin (seed account)
# Copy accessToken from response into adminToken in the environment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "LawrensuLeo@gmail.com",
  "password": "Minecraft26!"
}

###

### Refresh access token (requires active refresh cookie from login above)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh

###

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Forgot password (always returns 200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "LawrensuLeo@gmail.com"
}

###

### Set password with activation token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/set-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{activationToken}}",
  "password": "NewPassword123!"
}

###

### Resend activation email (account must be INACTIVE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/resend-activation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test-guide@example.com"
}
